    "GCNs typically consist of several layers, each performing convolution and aggregation steps to refine the node representations in the graph.",
    "By applying these layers iteratively, GCNs can capture complex patterns and dependencies within the graph data.Working of graph convolutional network A Graph Convolutional Network (GCN) is a type of neural network architecture designed for processing and analyzing graph-structured data.",
    "GCNs work by aggregating and propagating information through the nodes in a graph.",
